flowchart TD
    Caller[Phone Caller] --> TW[Twilio Voice]
    TW --> API[POST /twilio/voice/inbound]
    API --> WS[WebSocket Media Stream]

    WS --> VS[voice_stream.py]
    VS --> STT[AudioService.transcribe_audio]
    STT --> AM[AgentManager.chat]
    AM --> RP[RAGPipeline.query]
    RP --> LG[LangGraph Tools + Retrieval]
    LG --> TTS[TTSService.generate_speech]

    TTS --> VS --> TW --> Caller
